data.description:
MAJOR PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! This charming house is now available, and offers a wonderful opportunity for you to make it your new home. Located in the highly sought after community of Oak Ridge, offering a community pool, tennis courts and a club house for your enjoyment. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this property provides ample space for a growing family. Step inside and be greeted by the bright and airy atmosphere, created by the sparkling white tile floors throughout. The large master bedroom is a true retreat, offering a peaceful haven to relax and unwind. The entire home has been meticulously maintained and has been freshly painted inside, ensuring a clean and welcoming ambiance. The extra-large eat-in kitchen is perfect for those who love to cook and entertain. It features a long breakfast bar, providing plenty of space for gathering with friends and family. The open floor plan with high ceilings adds to the spaciousness of the home.
Both the master bedroom and bath boast generous proportions, including a large garden tub that invites you to indulge in a soothing soak after a long day; there are doors that lead from the master to a screened-in lanai, where you can enjoy the beautiful Florida weather while staying protected from any pesky bugs. The AC and water heater were recently replaced in 2020, ensuring efficiency and peace of mind.
If you have dreams of owning a pool, this property has room for one! Create your own backyard oasis and enjoy endless hours of fun and relaxation. PRICED TO SELL, so don't miss out on the opportunity to call this your new home. Schedule your showing today!
